# home/.mailcap
#
# Resources:
# https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mailcap
# http://linux.die.net/man/4/mailcap
# http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1524
# http://www.washington.edu/pine/faq/mailcap.sample
# http://www.mutt.org/doc/manual/manual-5.html
# http://www.mutt.org/doc/devel/manual.html#mailcap
# http://jasonwryan.com/blog/2012/05/12/mutt/
